      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/94aa30ae75b8c7c6a9c64ab05bd5dda7_3046385205672956030.png",
                "key": "迅捷禮刺劍",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "迅捷禮刺劍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素傷害</span>，本回合第一次使用此技能、且自身生命值不多於8時治療自身2點，但是附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">攻襲餘威</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">攻襲餘威</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>如果角色生命值至少為6，則受到2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/42bfd225eedc984bb1d4a4af99e3dcae_3302204850621087524.png",
                "key": "謎影障身法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "謎影障身法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">驚奇貓貓盒</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/b718fd9ceee2d78fdf5d76f345458f71_3190421685404711017.png",
                "key": "魔術·運變驚奇",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "魔術·運變驚奇"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">風元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方出戰角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害。（每回合1次）</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">我方角色受到</span><span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰</span>/<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水</span>/<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火</span>/<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">傷害時：</span>轉換此牌的元素類型，改為造成所受到的元素類型的傷害。（離場前僅限一次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_236008955770300524.png",
                "key": "驚奇貓貓盒",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/bc84abe7e3d8d79c9b75a0de329313dc_883721556257529711.png",
                "title": "驚奇貓貓盒"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附著的元素發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（冰）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（水）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（火）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">風元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擴散（雷）</span>：對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_8508703338471498298.png",
                "key": "風元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "風元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></p><p>每回合結束階段，<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/22/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_1794395139098325967.png",
